Tractor Supply Co. | Your Mesh Trailer Gift
                    TRACTOR SUPPLY CO.
                    OUT HERE, WE DO RIGHTTM
                    Member #
                    Your recent visit qualified you for a Carry-on Mesh Trailer gift
                    Because you shopped with Tractor Supply Co. in the last year, you’re eligible to receive a Carry-on Mesh Trailer at no cost — plus a $150 TSC Gift Card after a short 60-second survey.
                          ⏰ FINAL REMINDER
                          Your allocation closes at midnight tonight
                    Program details
                    400 mesh trailers · 400 digital cards · One per residence · No billing involved
                    Your member ID: TS--MESH · Status: Not yet claimed
              Key details on your Carry-on Mesh Trailer
                      • 1,500 lb hauling capacity
                      • Folds down flat for storage
                      • Rugged powder-coated steel frame
                      • Standard 2-inch coupler connection
                      • Durable mesh sidewall panels
                      • Integrated LED tail light wiring
                      • Safety chains come included
                      • Thoughtfully assembled in the USA
              Program timing is limited by supply and participation levels.
                          VIEW YOUR TRAILER + $150 CARD →
                    Survey lasts under 60 seconds · No purchase required to respond
              Availability is determined by overall program allocation. Trailer finish may vary by unit. $150 e-gift card is provided digitally once the survey is completed. This invitation is connected to your recent Tractor Supply Co. shopping activity.
              We appreciate your role in the Tractor Supply Co. community. Your input helps us better support those who live and work Out Here.
              At Tractor Supply, we know that keeping your land, animals, and equipment in top shape takes real dedication. That’s why we focus on dependable gear, practical solutions, and helpful advice from folks who understand life out here. Whether you’re tending a few backyard chickens or working several acres, the right tools make every day run smoother.
              From tractor attachments and trailers to fencing, feed, and workwear, our aisles are built for the way you live. We aim to offer sturdy products that stand up to long days, changing seasons, and tough conditions. When you pull into the lot or shop online, you’ll find brands you trust and value that fits real-world budgets.
              Our team members live in the same rural towns and farming communities you do, and they bring that experience to every conversation. Whether you’re setting up a new trailer, choosing the right hitch, or planning a fencing project, we’re here to lend a hand. Out here, neighbors help neighbors—and Tractor Supply is proud to be part of that tradition.
              Tractor Supply Co. · 5401 Virginia Way, Brentwood, TN 37027
              If you wish to stop getting these, feel free to exit here.
              --

